quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  42,16,"∆Åen wennjiroo…ìe hujjaaji meerente e diina Allah jippinaaka e Muhammadu kan, …ìaawo nde yim…ìe …ìen nootaade ka, hujja …ìen on, ko meere yanoowo ka Joomi ma…ì…ìe e ka gom…óim…ìe …ìen; …ìa…óte woo alanaa mo. Tikkere Allah hino fawii …ìe, sabu yeddugol …ìe ngol saloo goonga, hino woodani …ìe lepte sa…ótu…óe, sabbitii…óe …ìe √ëalnde Darngal."
  42,17,"Ko Allah woni jippinir…óo Alqur'aanaare nden goonga, mo sikke alaa e mu'un, O jippini kadi fii nun…óal, ko √±aawiree hakkunde yim…ìe …ìen. Hino hasii hara Darngal, ngal …ìee fennata fii mun ngal, ko ko …ìadii. Hino anndaa non, wonnde kala ko arata, ko ko hewti."
  42,18,"∆Åe gom…óinaa …ìen Darngal, hino …óa…ì…ìa yaccingol fii maggal; tawde …ìe gom…óinaa fii hasboore wanaa warjeede wanaa fii lepte. Gom…óim…ìe Allah …ìen kan, ko …ìe hulu …ìe fii maggal, e hoore hi…ìe felliti wonnde ko ngal goonga, mo sikke alaa e mu'un. Awa anndee won…ìe yeddondireede …ìen e fii Darngal, hara hi…ìe sikkitii daragol maggal, ko pellet, …ìe wonii e nder majjere wo…ó…óunde goonga."
  42,19,"Allah ko newanii…óo jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen. Himo yaacnana arsika mo O muuyani e ma…ì…ìe, O …ìillina mo O muuyani, ka yurmegol mo; hay si go…ó…óum goo yaltitii. Ko Kanko woni Doolnu…óo Mo gooto foolataa, Jaalii…óo yagginoowo ay…ìe Makko …ìen."
  42,20,"Kala taw…óo ko baraaje ndun laakara o faaliraa golle makko …óen, Men sowanay mo mbarjaari makko ndin; mo∆¥∆¥ere kala, sappo yeru mun, haa hewta cowalle teeme…ó…óe jee…ói…ói, haa …ìura …óon ko …óuu…ói. Kala kadi taw…óo ko jayru ndun aduna tun o faalaa, Men okkay mo ge…ìal makko ngal, yeru makko on; hara non o alaa ka laakara ton, hay ge…ìal, tawde o …ìuurnii aduna e dow laakara."
  42,21,"Kaa hara kafidaa…ói e Alalh hino woodani …ìee sirkoo…ìe, sar'inan…ói …ìe e diina kan, kon ko Allah du≈ãaaki fi mun: harmingol ko dagii, maa dagingol ko harmi? Si wanaano fii ngola Konngol ngol Allah happunoo e mun, dumunna senndugoygol hakkunde luutondir…ìe …ìen, e tawde O nennanay …ìe haa nden √±lande, O √±aawayno hakkunde ma…ì…ìe kisan. Ko pellet, hino woodani too√±ir…ìe ko'e-mun …ìen sirkangol Allah yedda Mo, lepte muusu…óe, √ëalnde Darngal."
  42,22,"A yi'ay an Nulaa…óo, too√±ir…ìe ko'e-mun …ìen sirku e geddi, hi…ìe huliri leptireede ko …ìe faggitii kon e bakkaatu, hara le …óum yantay e ma…ì…ìe, feere mun alaa, nafa woo alaa e ko …ìe hulirta …óum. ∆Åen non gom…óim…ìe Allah e Nulaa…óo Makko on, …ìe golli golle mo∆¥∆¥e, …ìen no seedi e …ìeya; …ìee …óoo hino e nder naakooji Aljanna, hi…ìe neeminora ton, kala ko …ìe faalaa ka Joomi ma…ì…ìe; neemaaji …ói ta∆¥ondirtaa haa pooma. Ko …óum tigiri, woni …ìural mawnungal, ngal alaa nanndo."